Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:04.25,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}FLYING IN THE SKY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:09.19,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最高的地方 馳騁於空中的任何角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.92,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.90,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀著光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:16.32,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮大地的盡頭呼喚奇跡的咒語 {\fnComic Sans MS}SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:25.44,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不遲疑的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:31.72,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有無限的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:39.08,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論嘗試多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:47.51,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼痛苦都貫徹到底{\fnComic Sans MS}（G GUNDAM）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:50.63,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛隨時都充斥於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.21,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:00:57.32,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙手 咆哮著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:01.31,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向明天飛奔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:03.10,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}BRIGHT YOU NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:08.06,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所描繪的未來之藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:09.80,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:11.60,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:15.34,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部如你所願 {\fnComic Sans MS}I GET A CHANCE！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些上天恩賜的細小水滴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前起便一直賜予我們情趣與憂愁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時很溫柔，有時卻很殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，今宵這場雨會灑在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個男人和一個女人的過去上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人會被怎樣的命運弄濕呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒下這場雨就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人或許會那樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，今日的對手是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Turkey的Minaret Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs56}雨中再會…FALLING RAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傳聞我聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一星期前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這國家的GUNDAM突然四處搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把伊斯坦堡的西部破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事傳遍全世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便會成為國家的恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武裝警察正拚命找他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那完全無用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝會看穿一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相早晚會揭曉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙真遲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我已習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，我讀醫學部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他讀機械工學部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他是摔跤會的教練
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我讀衛星大學時的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同級同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我別打擾他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM的起動鎖匙！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在這種地方重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這裡是你的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到你也不出奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你還記得這裡是我的故鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說那些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要快點替你診治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，給手臂我看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Gundam的細胞！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Gundam和京二·卡休一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡到地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們調查卡休博士的研究室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能找到線索以便\N定下將來對付Devil Gundam的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而根據我們發現的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們看見一件可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們現在注射入老鼠體內的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有問題的Devil Gundam細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡稱DG細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人震驚的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不只是一種金屬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它也能和有機物質結合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有生命的細胞一樣在體內擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後經過一段潛伏期
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚便會開始變成金屬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這階段還能治療
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但萬一腦部被侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就會被Devil Gundam所控制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複進行破壞與殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底變成他的木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這方法來增加自己的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是卡休博士造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Gundam三大理論機能之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我增殖！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而最可怕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一我們人類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到這種DG細胞的感染
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們人類恐怕會有同一結果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一結果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵，莉茵？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嚇一了跳？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是一直以來的老毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已經開始康復
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之，讓我詳細檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹是個醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特，我求你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以答應我一件事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你不要告訴任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生有義務為病人保守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這階段還能治療
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但萬一腦部被侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就會重複進行破壞與殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞與殺戮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼也不問我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為每一個人都有其苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的雨真不方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道何時會停雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FALLING RAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星裡這樣稱呼預知的下雨天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來，當日也是下雨天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵？你的名字原來叫莉茵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，爸爸說雨是對大地的恩賜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說我起這名字是要我像雨一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為滋潤大地的女性，很誇張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那個下雨天之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你便從我面前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，我很久之後才聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經回到neo Japan的衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但當日，我無論如何一定要見你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們能這樣子重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫多蒙的是你男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是你丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是工作上的拍檔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞…塞伊特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…捨棄我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？你那麼匆忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真怪呢，根本沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人是Gundam Fighter吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙，你想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要問他在哪裡遇上Devil Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使要進行GUNDAM FIGHT也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有病啊，我不會讓他那樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你不是我的拍檔嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同時也是醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為醫生的不可讓病人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出令病情惡化的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為醫生…真的只是那樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你鬱鬱不歡，讓女人跑了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人能逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都像籠中鳥一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你離開後我便馬上成為Gundam Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在機械工學的知識\N和學生時代的摔跤招式給看中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直埋頭於戰鬥與破壞裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此便和你這種善良的人無緣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，某一日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的力量很可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有反抗的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸個一敗塗地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我醒來時，他已經不知所蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我操縱GUNDAM時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有時會好像失去意識一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去意識？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一次，當我醒覺時…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本應為祖國尊嚴而戰的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的故鄉破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏起GUNDAM四處躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來失去知覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來後就見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神的牽引嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候注射鎮靜劑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道何時又會發作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你出去會馬上被捉住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我繼續留在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或許會殺了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是醫生啊，我不能捨棄病人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當日本來打算見你決定一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇成為Gundam Fighter平步青雲？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是留在研究院和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當日沒來是因為討厭了我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來給他們找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料，部隊開始集結起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們知道你們窩藏我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你們也會被捉住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去引開他們的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們趁機逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去！塞伊特…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追！別放過他！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了，莉茵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DG細胞開始活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是叫我去救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Gundam參加FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使對方是誰也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眾神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也喜歡諷刺的命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至少以GUNDAM FIGHT決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Gundam的自我再生！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙！塞伊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！塞伊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走！他已經是惡魔的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是你認識的塞伊特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特的腦還未被DG細胞感染
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能跟你比賽就是證明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他聽到我的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就有可能回復清醒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求你，聽我講
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當日的事，我記得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FALLING RAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和預測一樣下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也打算前去約定的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，有點困難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡休世伯他…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙？他回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接到爸爸的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要馬上回去neo Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並非因為討厭了你，所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特，我求你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變回我喜歡的你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求你！塞伊特！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開！莉茵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒它只有這機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…不要殺死塞伊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！我再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Devil Gundam有關的人一定要死！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使對方是誰也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不留下來可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府知道塞伊特有病後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特也就不會被重判吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的交給這裡的醫院便行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身為醫生的工作結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在再次變回你的拍擋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你，多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:21:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想把Devil Gundam的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給這國家罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:31.50,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便數千的日夜流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:35.89,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所到達的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:40.33,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨著 追求著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:43.90,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫步著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:51.05,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人啊 在我瞳孔的深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:56.75,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實搖曳著的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:23:02.06,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何傳達才好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:08.54,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓受傷的心與身體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:12.72,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這溫暖的懷抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.85,0:23:18.71,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比海更深沉的睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在因神秘MS軍團而變為廢墟的東京
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.26,0:23:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙和莉茵被一名格鬥家救了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不正是多蒙的師傅 前代King Of Heart嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動武鬥傳G GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.64,0:23:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫東方不敗！Master Asia出場
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.04,0:23:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！


